OL,3,CWater companies reach highest level of
OL,4,Cpollution in a decade, say campaigners
OL,6,FSAS's Chief Executive Giles Bristow
OL,7,Fsays his group reflects the public
OL,8,Fanger at UK water companies
OL,10,FWater companies in England recorded
OL,11,F2,487 pollution incidents last year `
OL,12,Fmore than double the target set by the
OL,13,FEnvironment Agency, according to
OL,14,Fcampaigners.
OL,16,FFirms were collectively set a target
OL,17,Fof a 40% reduction in pollution
OL,18,Fincidents but instead recorded a 30%
OL,19,Fincrease, Surfers Against Sewage (SAS)
OL,20,Fsaid, based on freedom of information
OL,21,Fdata.
