OL,3,CWater companies reach highest level of
OL,4,Cpollution in a decade, say campaigners
OL,6,FThis was the first full year that 100%
OL,7,Fof storm overflows had been monitored
OL,8,Fand the figures revealed that although
OL,9,Fthe number of spills fell slightly
OL,10,Fcompared with 2023, the duration of
OL,11,Fsewage discharges was up.
OL,13,FThese spills should only take place in
OL,14,F"exceptional circumstances" to prevent
OL,15,Fsewers from being overwhelmed in heavy
OL,16,Frainfall and backing up into homes.
