OL,3,CWater companies reach highest level of
OL,4,Cpollution in a decade, say campaigners
OL,6,FA survey for SAS suggests that more
OL,7,Fthan a quarter of adults in England
OL,8,F(27%) have considered withholding
OL,9,Fwater bill payments due to anger with
OL,10,Fthe actions of their suppliers.
OL,12,FJust one-third of respondents believe
OL,13,Fthat their water supplier will take
OL,14,Fthe necessary action to end sewage
OL,15,Fpollution.
OL,17,FSAS said it received 1,853 sickness
OL,18,Freports through its Safer Seas &
OL,19,FRivers Service app last year ` an
OL,20,Faverage of five people a day.
