OL,3,CWater companies reach highest level of
OL,4,Cpollution in a decade, say campaigners
OL,6,FSAS's Chief Executive, Giles Bristow,
OL,7,Fshares this frustration. He said: "The
OL,8,Fnumbers are staggering: record hours
OL,9,Fof sewage discharges, huge bill
OL,10,Fincreases, thousands of people
OL,11,Fbecoming ill and yet still the
OL,12,Findustry has the gall to still pay out
OL,13,Fbillions of billpayer money to
OL,14,Fshareholders.
OL,16,F"Things could not be clearer: this
OL,17,Fbroken system needs urgent and radical
OL,18,Freform.
